### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order. Each must succeed before proceeding to the next.

1. `dotnet build sdk/communication/Azure.Communication.Messages/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/communication/Azure.Communication.Messages/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 communication` — check `git diff` afterward to confirm README was updated with snippet content
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 communication` — regenerates API listing files; required if any public types or members were changed
5. `dotnet format sdk/communication/Azure.Communication.Messages/`

